## Critical Rules

1. **Single source of truth:** Edit `directives/SOP.md` or `.agent/hints/`, then run `python tools/sync_configs.py`
2. **Never hand-edit** generated files: `CLAUDE.md`, `AGENT.md`, `GEMINI.md`, `.cursorrules`, `.claudecode.md`
3. Run `python tools/verify_{{DOMAIN}}.py` before completing any task

## Quick Commands

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `python tools/verify_{{DOMAIN}}.py` | Run verification checks |
| `python tools/sync_configs.py` | Regenerate all AI configs |

## Skill Commands (gstack)

[gstack](https://github.com/garrytan/gstack) provides 25 specialized workflow skills — each acts as a distinct specialist role. Invoke them individually (not as `/gstack`).

| Skill | Role | Purpose |
|-------|------|---------|
| `/office-hours` | YC partner | Brainstorming and idea validation |
| `/plan-ceo-review` | Founder | Challenge assumptions, find the 10-star version of the plan |
| `/plan-eng-review` | Eng manager | Lock architecture, edge cases, data flow |
| `/plan-design-review` | Designer | Rate design dimensions 0-10, fix plan to reach 10 |
| `/design-consultation` | Design lead | Create complete design system (DESIGN.md) |
| `/design-review` | Visual QA | Find and fix visual inconsistencies and AI slop |
| `/investigate` | Root cause analyst | Systematic debugging — no fixes without root cause |
| `/browse` | Browser automation | Headless browser: navigate, click, screenshot, test forms |
| `/freeze` | Scope limiter | Restrict edits to a specific directory |
| `/unfreeze` | Scope restorer | Clear freeze boundary, allow all edits |
| `/careful` | Safety guard | Warn before destructive commands |
| `/guard` | Full safety | Combines `/careful` + `/freeze` |
| `/qa` | QA lead | Systematic QA testing — find, fix, verify bugs |
| `/qa-only` | QA reporter | Report-only QA without fixes |
| `/benchmark` | Perf engineer | Performance regression detection with Web Vitals |
| `/setup-browser-cookies` | Session manager | Import cookies for authenticated `/browse` and `/qa` sessions |
| `/review` | Code reviewer | Pre-landing code review focused on production failure modes |
| `/codex` | Second opinion | Independent code review via OpenAI Codex |
| `/ship` | Release engineer | Run tests, create PR, deploy in one command |
| `/land-and-deploy` | Deploy engineer | Merge PR, wait for CI, verify production health |
| `/setup-deploy` | Deploy config | Configure deployment platform and health checks |
| `/canary` | Post-deploy monitor | Watch live app for errors after deploy |
| `/document-release` | Tech writer | Post-ship docs update synced with what shipped |
| `/retro` | Team lead | Sprint/task retrospective with per-person feedback |
| `/gstack-upgrade` | Updater | Upgrade gstack to latest version |
